achievement-started-recruiting =
  .title = Started Recruiting
  .desc = It is time.
 
 You start carefully asking around,
 checking web forums with likeminded people,
 discreetly contacting people who are asking the right questions,
 all in an effort to find people who might join you
 in your investigations into the deeper truths.

achievement-first-minion-recruit =
  .title = Your First Minion
  .desc = You have recruited your first follower, a minion.

 Minions will be loyal contributors to your cult and are sworn to secrecy.
 One day you may be able to initiate a Minion into the deeper mysteries,
 and have them become a fellow Priest of your cult.
